## Problem Statement

The system has 17 persistent databases but is **mostly memoryless**:
- 8/17 have data, only 4/17 are read back into decisions
- All 16 checkers use `period='1d'` — zero multi-day context
- NarrativeBrain has 8 empty tables, never writes
- DP Learning has 372 interactions but 0 learned patterns
- No checker knows its own accuracy

