### S1.3 — Health Registry Persistence

**Problem:** 2 rows. Resets each deploy.

**Grep receipt:**
```
checker_health.py:57: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS checker_runs  ← uses IF NOT EXISTS, so NOT dropping
checker_health.py:178: INSERT INTO checker_runs  ← appends
